Package ca.openosp.openo.commn.model

Class CdsClientFormData

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.commn.model.AbstractModel<Integer>
ca.openosp.openo.commn.model.CdsClientFormData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class CdsClientFormData extends AbstractModel<Integer> implements Serializable
This entity represents key value pairs associated with the CdsClientForm object. Generally speaking the key is the question asked and is specified by us, the answer is generally the CDS category like "010-4" or something like that.
